name: live-sports-project-root
description: Root package for Live Sports Project

scripts.build-proto: npm install grpc-web protobufjs && node ./frontend/node_modules/protobufjs/bin/pbjs -t static-module -w commonjs --keep-case -o ./frontend/proto/match_pb_messages.js -p ./match-service/proto -p /usr/include/google/protobuf ./match-service/proto/match.proto && node ./frontend/node_modules/protobufjs/bin/pbts -o ./frontend/proto/match_pb_messages.d.ts ./frontend/proto/match_pb_messages.js && node ./frontend/node_modules/protobufjs/bin/pbjs -t static-module -w commonjs --keep-case -o ./frontend/proto/google_protobuf_empty_pb.js -p /usr/include/google/protobuf /usr/include/google/protobuf/empty.proto
